Plant Height

Most visual difference is in week 6 (w6)

d1 <- d0[d0$Week == "W6" , c("Treatment", "Species", "Plant_height") ]
d1 <- na.exclude(d1) #remove the ones with empty cells 
lm1 <- lm(Plant_height ~ Treatment + Species, data=d1)
anova(lm1)
